          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="attention-section">
        <h1><i class="icon-comments"></i> Discussion</h1>
        <div>At the end of the session, have participants present their new webpages, explain their work process and what they learned.
<p>How do you see yourself as a coder or webmaker?</p>
          <p>What inspires you about technology?</p>
          <p>What questions do you have about how the Web works or how you can learn to build the Web?</p>
      </div>
      </section>
